<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5ab838d7-2ca8-46fc-83ee-be93b22d137f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-924f7db8-44a6-4b20-bc95-e1485f12f32e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">면지는 구분을 위해 넣거나 페이지의 짝수가 안맞을 때 간지처럼 삽입하는 경우를 말합니다. 다른 색깔의 종이를 삽입하는것은 구분을 위해 주로 많이 사용되며 특히 표지 앞뒤로 면지를 넣어 구분하는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cab4e90d-5853-4d33-bef3-7e17f14bba3d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-684ff71e-60dc-4588-ba1c-ce666968969f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-0a2c747b-35c8-4ba6-89ea-2e7f670aad1a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5792386a-d625-4216-a63b-c3d6313f0201\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd45183e-71cd-45b7-8508-0cc957dff6b4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b1c340f3-f432-4307-a543-62ca337a43df\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3a1d558a-a1ef-49bd-902c-591ea5d98665\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-3a1d558a-a1ef-49bd-902c-591ea5d98665\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMDJfOTYg/MDAxNjY3MzgxODk2MTE5.o7HVaYA49qv1YdiWPoOQggrHnGbqL6hoqR-sPz01ZXMg.6AOBDajqirZ_fkz7i7ZWwUdUkTTriwdB2dVDu38Ej10g.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%9A%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A1%9D_%EC%B1%85%EC%9E%90.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1417\", \"originalHeight\" : \"945\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMDJfOTYg/MDAxNjY3MzgxODk2MTE5.o7HVaYA49qv1YdiWPoOQggrHnGbqL6hoqR-sPz01ZXMg.6AOBDajqirZ_fkz7i7ZWwUdUkTTriwdB2dVDu38Ej10g.PNG.cookthedesign/%ED%9A%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A1%9D_%EC%B1%85%EC%9E%90.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9ca6a455-97d3-4549-8448-8c85df10fcf0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5956b44f-5508-4891-830a-74e562dd4c61\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fdc586e5-ad18-4edc-bbaa-d57276d2d7ff\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">인쇄는 조판에 따라 변경되지만 보통 4배수나 8배수로 컬러를 구분합니다. 본 예제는 흑백 256pages로 국전지 16대로 인쇄를 작업했습니다. 컬러인 경우 130pages로 국전 8대 돈땡으로 작업되었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f6f86ef5-8058-41fe-b5d5-6f25e79bcf12\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-77ad5651-34a4-407f-a082-d08ea3744189\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-33ec2bdd-9edf-4ed2-9e98-f5c6c733708d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-47e8f0bb-b271-4ff1-999e-72bc33ca0023\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">총 수량은 500부 인쇄하였으며 표지는 CR코팅으로 처리하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-62d3808f-510b-44c3-a687-06523df1d80a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0326fab5-6236-4974-b1a7-2d593a49d902\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-93c6a8f0-6997-4c00-a8bc-d80564c8c78f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6f89fd5c-cfed-4faf-be3a-b3e119c60286\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">책자나 기타 인쇄에 궁금하신 사항이 있으면 언제든지 문의주십시요.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2df5d2a4-cccc-4ca5-af13-9b5dfdaa6134\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4249a7f5-0fe2-4b15-86df-0b26317155d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-64eaeb33-a30d-4412-979e-b23b9f247a9e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F222917806042#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
